name: AAU-SSW
short_description: This site is developed to avail teaching materials to students of School of Social Work at Addis Ababa University. Different published articles, book chapters, and books will be available to students. This site will also be used as a means to have open discussion about Social Work profession in general and Social Work education in particular. Professors at different Universities will be invited to contribute their materials so that students can have access. .........................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................
summary: This site is developed to avail teaching materials to students of SSW
